  "body": "We need a metric to track how \"busy\" our node is.\r\n\r\nA potential approach would be to track async event loop lag:\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nsetInterval(async () => {\r\n  const startTime = Date.now();\r\n  await sleep(0);\r\n  const asyncEventLoopLag = Date.now() - startTime;\r\n}, 1000)\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n_Originally posted by @dapplion in https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/2952#issuecomment-907635918_",
